Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.69,0:00:04.76,OP-Ch,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9\fad(130,130)}「没有你的未来」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.06,0:00:16.86,OP-JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(130,130)}守るべきものなんて
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.87,0:00:26.21,OP-JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(130,130)}悩むまでもなく一つしかなかった
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.58,0:00:30.36,OP-JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(130,130)}叫び声のこだま
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.38,0:00:39.63,OP-JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(130,130)}むなしく響いた 深い森の奥に
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.30,0:00:46.21,OP-JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(130,130)}涙をこらえられた理由は
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.16,0:00:52.75,OP-JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(130,130)}重ねた指のぬくもりのせい
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.08,0:00:56.00,OP-JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(130,130)}君がいない未来
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.01,0:00:59.11,OP-JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(130,130)}意味などない未来
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.83,0:01:05.17,OP-JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(130,130)}二度と離したりはしないから
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.89,0:01:09.74,OP-JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(130,130)}君と臨む世界
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.79,0:01:12.45,OP-JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(130,130)}見たことない世界
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.48,0:01:19.87,OP-JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(130,130)}時空を越えて はるか旅する僕等
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.06,0:00:16.86,OP-Ch,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(130,130)}必须要守护的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.87,0:00:26.21,OP-Ch,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(130,130)}根本不用费心思考 本来就只有一个
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.58,0:00:30.36,OP-Ch,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(130,130)}呐喊的回音
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.38,0:00:39.63,OP-Ch,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(130,130)}在幽深的森林深处 空虚地回荡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.30,0:00:46.21,OP-Ch,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(130,130)}能够忍住眼泪的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.16,0:00:52.75,OP-Ch,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(130,130)}是与你十指相扣的温暖
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.08,0:00:56.00,OP-Ch,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(130,130)}没有你的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.01,0:00:59.11,OP-Ch,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(130,130)}毫无意义的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.83,0:01:05.17,OP-Ch,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(130,130)}我不会再远你而去
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.89,0:01:09.74,OP-Ch,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(130,130)}与你共赴的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.79,0:01:12.45,OP-Ch,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(130,130)}未曾见过的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.48,0:01:19.87,OP-Ch,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(130,130)}穿越时空 我们继续漫长的旅途
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.65,0:22:05.26,ED-JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(130,130)}遠い道の先で あなたの事をずっと想う
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.28,0:22:12.70,ED-JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(130,130)}昨日のように感じる 出逢い忘れはしない
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.71,0:22:20.05,ED-JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(130,130)}遠い道の先に あなたがいれば見つめ合える
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.12,0:22:28.33,ED-JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(130,130)}変わらぬ愛守る そう 永遠に忘れはしない
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.55,0:22:34.68,ED-JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(130,130)}Oh 寂しさで 時が流れなくなっても
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.15,0:22:42.25,ED-JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(130,130)}Oh どの道も あなたへと続いてるから
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.59,0:22:45.69,ED-JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(130,130)}悲しみはすぐに捨てるの
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.92,0:22:51.15,ED-JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(130,130)}ここには 涙色の君映らないけど
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.22,0:22:55.70,ED-JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(130,130)}今を生きる私の姿だけ届いて欲しい
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.83,0:23:05.23,ED-JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(130,130)}振り返ればきっと 二人の歩幅遠のくから
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.33,0:23:13.10,ED-JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(130,130)}結び合った運命よ 今は解きはしない
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.21,0:23:20.25,ED-JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(130,130)}遠い道の先で あなたの事をずっと想う
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.36,0:23:28.75,ED-JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(130,130)}あなたと二人 嘘のない世界築ける きっと
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.65,0:22:05.26,ED-Ch,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(130,130)}在遥远的前路上 我一直思念着你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.28,0:22:12.70,ED-Ch,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(130,130)}恍如昨日的邂逅 我不会忘记
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.71,0:22:20.05,ED-Ch,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(130,130)}在遥远的前路上 你若能与我相伴 便能互相注视
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.12,0:22:28.33,ED-Ch,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(130,130)}守护不变的爱 永远不会忘记
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.55,0:22:34.68,ED-Ch,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(130,130)}Oh 寂寞 即使让时间停止
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.15,0:22:42.25,ED-Ch,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(130,130)}Oh 无论哪条路 都与你相通
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.59,0:22:45.69,ED-Ch,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(130,130)}因此我可以马上忘记悲伤
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.92,0:22:51.15,ED-Ch,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(130,130)}这里 没有映现着落泪的你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.22,0:22:55.70,ED-Ch,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(130,130)}但请把我现在活着的身姿 传递给你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.83,0:23:05.23,ED-Ch,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(130,130)}回过头看 两人的步伐必定远离
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.33,0:23:13.10,ED-Ch,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(130,130)}结合的命运 现在请不要解开
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.21,0:23:20.25,ED-Ch,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(130,130)}在遥远的前路上 我一直思念着你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.36,0:23:28.75,ED-Ch,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(130,130)}只要与你 定能筑起没有谎言的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.66,0:22:01.89,ED-Ch,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9\fad(130,130)}「在遙遠的前路上」
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.30,0:01:38.63,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,聚齐了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.59,0:01:44.04,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,互称同伴的无聊家伙们
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.57,0:01:52.69,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,没有一个人缺席
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.88,0:02:04.59,Title,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(130,300)}无法传达的思念
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.10,0:02:14.80,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,枫大人 那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.34,0:02:17.40,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,奈落正在崩垮
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.50,0:02:19.53,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,风穴
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.08,0:02:20.81,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,飞来骨
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.60,0:02:24.56,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,冥道残月破
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.84,0:02:27.96,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,爆碎牙
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.48,0:02:38.69,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,奈落自己将身体割离了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.06,0:02:42.11,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,是打算逃开爆碎牙的破坏吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.42,0:02:44.52,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,哼 白费功夫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.37,0:02:52.63,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,四魂之玉的光芒…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.63,0:02:56.18,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,还真是群天真的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.59,0:03:00.96,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,只是同伴到齐了 就能让四魂之玉恢复光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.67,0:03:04.75,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是你们所谓的希望吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.24,0:03:11.33,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,但是别忘了 四魂之玉已经和我奈落合为一体
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.85,0:03:14.84,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,黑暗击退了光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.70,0:03:23.45,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,混蛋 到底还是让玉吞噬了心智吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.70,0:03:27.25,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,又是瘴气团
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.31,0:03:31.09,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,冥道残月破
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.45,0:03:38.37,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶 明明都完全砍中了 他却死不了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.65,0:03:42.03,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,看来四魂之玉相当执着于这个世界啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.12,0:03:43.30,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,下面也有
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.51,0:03:44.35,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,无聊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.80,0:03:45.82,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,爆碎牙
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.79,0:03:54.34,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,每次破坏后就会释放出比之前更加强烈的瘴气
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.97,0:03:55.51,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,邪见
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.86,0:03:56.93,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.36,0:03:58.99,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,到奈落体外去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.45,0:03:59.95,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.47,0:04:02.16,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,我一直在等这句话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.49,0:04:02.99,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.00,0:04:06.98,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,还不明白吗 你们两个在这里只会碍事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.44,0:04:08.39,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,杀生丸大人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.26,0:04:11.15,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,外面也有
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.47,0:04:12.28,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,飞来骨
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.89,0:04:13.64,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.13,0:04:16.13,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,琥珀 快点到外面去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.87,0:04:20.30,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,珊瑚大人 谢谢你给我防毒面具
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.20,0:04:21.73,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,铃
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.60,0:04:28.99,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,法师大人 请戴上这个
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.03,0:04:30.56,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,琥珀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.58,0:04:33.32,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐就拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.03,0:04:34.80,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.55,0:04:36.62,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧 珊瑚
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.80,0:04:37.30,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.26,0:04:43.86,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,被好强的瘴气包围着
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.35,0:04:46.96,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然和刚开始看到的大小一样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.27,0:04:48.91,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,但里面已经空空如也
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.94,0:04:53.14,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,而且正在坠落 这个方向是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.00,0:04:55.99,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,风穴
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.72,0:05:00.35,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,不管怎么吸 瘴气还是会不断涌出
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.82,0:05:02.31,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.51,0:05:03.65,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,没事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.28,0:05:07.82,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然很不可思议 但我身边的瘴气似乎都被净化了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.34,0:05:12.88,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,不过 每次只要一拉弓就会被奈落妨碍
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.31,0:05:14.99,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,明明只要把箭射出去就能射中的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.63,0:05:18.23,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,不会让你射的 现在还不行
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.87,0:05:20.53,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,冥道残月破
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.71,0:05:21.63,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,爆碎牙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.69,0:05:27.66,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,就差一点 就差一点了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.15,0:05:31.19,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,不好了 枫大人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.65,0:05:32.77,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,朝这边来了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.88,0:05:35.45,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,大家快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.46,0:05:36.56,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,是…是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.42,0:05:41.65,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,对奈落和鬼蜘蛛来说 这个村庄是宿命之地
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.36,0:05:44.40,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙该不会是想将这个村子…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.03,0:05:48.24,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,冥道残月破
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.79,0:05:53.30,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,没用的 奈落
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.67,0:05:57.68,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,你越是抵抗 你身体就被削去更多
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.02,0:06:01.51,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,身体还有很多
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.84,0:06:04.13,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,足够毁坏一个村子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.40,0:06:05.16,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,你说村子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.43,0:06:10.55,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,瘴气掉到地上了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.92,0:06:24.40,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,碰到瘴气会尸骨无存的 快点逃走
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.81,0:06:26.52,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,奈落 你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.97,0:06:30.66,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,连你们自己在哪里都不知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.67,0:06:33.27,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,已经晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.64,0:06:38.89,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,如果杀了我 我充满瘴气的遗骸就会落到村中
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.92,0:06:42.61,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,那又怎么样 爆碎牙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.76,0:06:48.46,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,崩塌了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.48,0:06:52.26,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,四魂之玉还活着
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.17,0:06:54.31,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,遵从奈落的意志坠落下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.51,0:06:58.61,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,七宝 能到外面去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.71,0:06:59.69,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,哦…嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.11,0:07:01.63,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,珊瑚 我们也出去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.02,0:07:02.52,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.11,0:07:06.98,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,就算是爆碎牙 也无法砍碎四魂之玉吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.69,0:07:09.82,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,风穴
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.73,0:07:21.03,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,冥道残月破
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.60,0:07:33.11,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.97,0:07:34.81,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,现在的话能射出去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.61,0:07:39.82,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,相信自己 能射中的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.59,0:07:43.39,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,我的箭能射穿四魂之玉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.50,0:07:49.60,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,箭消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.23,0:07:52.37,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托了 一定要射中玉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.54,0:08:00.35,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,四魂之玉没有实现你真正的愿望吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.35,0:08:03.21,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,你说我真正的愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.50,0:08:05.28,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.34,0:08:11.06,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是想得到桔梗的心罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.93,0:08:17.51,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,看来就算到了那个世界
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.93,0:08:22.88,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,也没办法和桔梗同去一个地方啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.32,0:08:39.51,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,瘴气团…正在消失
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.33,0:08:43.53,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,村子周围的瘴气正在被净化
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.00,0:08:46.63,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇小姐的箭击败了奈落
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.13,0:08:47.90,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.37,0:08:50.96,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.91,0:08:54.53,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.56,0:08:55.37,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.28,0:09:04.79,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.66,0:09:15.16,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,奈落
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.79,0:09:28.54,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,我那个时候向四魂之玉许下了愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.02,0:09:29.65,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,那个时候…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.21,0:09:33.82,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,梦幻之白夜挥刀砍你的那个时候
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.67,0:09:36.54,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,被白夜砍到了？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.99,0:09:41.93,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,在我死去的同时 那个愿望应该能够实现
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.54,0:09:47.84,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,玉让我许下的 四魂之玉自己的愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.14,0:09:52.75,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,奈落
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.80,0:10:09.70,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,法师大人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.69,0:10:12.52,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,风穴消失了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.90,0:10:14.65,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,诅咒解除了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.30,0:10:18.84,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,没错 奈落已经不在了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.88,0:10:23.98,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,什…冥道
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.23,0:10:25.90,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.21,0:10:26.80,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.91,0:10:32.56,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.51,0:10:35.25,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,冥道消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.55,0:10:38.35,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,到…到底怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.71,0:10:39.40,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.04,0:10:43.18,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇被白夜砍中了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.56,0:10:45.31,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.79,0:10:47.28,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,我看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.90,0:10:52.04,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,梦幻之白夜偷取冥道残月破妖力的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.27,0:10:55.11,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,井呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.14,0:10:56.78,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,枫大人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.51,0:10:59.28,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,食骨之井怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.37,0:11:09.00,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,井消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.97,0:11:17.13,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,草太
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.75,0:11:20.75,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇还是身体不好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.51,0:11:24.02,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,连高中的入学式都没有来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.37,0:11:27.54,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 这么虚弱还真是让人烦恼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.94,0:11:30.38,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.03,0:11:33.79,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,说了入学式之前一定会回来的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.23,0:11:37.67,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了 地震？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.96,0:11:40.76,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,不是 好像是什么从祠堂中…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.69,0:11:42.63,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,什么什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.25,0:11:45.11,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,等等 不能随便看的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.37,0:11:45.29,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,是不是里面坍塌了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.64,0:11:53.07,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈 爷爷 不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.37,0:11:59.26,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,食骨之井消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.02,0:12:01.64,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.49,0:12:11.49,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,或许戈薇已经回到井对面的世界了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.87,0:12:16.00,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,不 如果奈落想除去戈薇的话
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.53,0:12:18.06,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,他应该更早之前就能动手了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.58,0:12:22.19,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,但是他却特意朝着村里的井这边来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.61,0:12:25.85,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,奈落最后到底许了什么愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.04,0:12:33.38,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉 四魂之玉怎么样了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.57,0:12:35.72,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,四魂之玉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.42,0:12:40.24,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托了 铁碎牙
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.67,0:12:42.29,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,带我去戈薇那里
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.57,0:12:43.16,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.73,0:12:46.90,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,冥道残月破
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.62,0:12:55.06,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,四魂之玉在惧怕戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.93,0:12:59.53,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,如果四魂之玉想要存在下来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.67,0:13:02.15,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,就不可能会让戈薇平安无事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.81,0:13:04.16,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,等着我 戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.66,0:13:06.28,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,我一定会把你找出来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.93,0:13:24.06,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 在那儿
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.26,0:13:25.37,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.68,0:13:28.46,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,大家…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.96,0:13:29.70,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.35,0:13:31.43,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,陪我们去买东西吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.79,0:13:32.97,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,一起去看看运动装吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.87,0:13:37.48,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,对了 我现在已经是高中生了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.86,0:13:43.45,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,话说回来 你怎么样了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.73,0:13:44.46,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,拒绝了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.82,0:13:46.11,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 为什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.37,0:13:48.01,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,交往一下多好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.39,0:13:51.25,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,不行 他比我还矮呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.45,0:13:52.39,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 这倒也是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.72,0:13:56.06,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,被告白了啊 是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.93,0:13:59.65,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,就是入学式时来搭讪的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.89,0:14:01.88,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇你当时不也在场吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.35,0:14:03.60,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 是这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.66,0:14:06.25,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,入学式
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.96,0:14:12.21,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇 快来帮个忙
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.84,0:14:14.45,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,已经决定加入哪个社团了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.64,0:14:16.15,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 网球部
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.68,0:14:17.72,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,对了 爷爷
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.08,0:14:19.85,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,快点给我庆祝升入高中的礼物
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.04,0:14:22.19,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 不是已经给了你吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.54,0:14:27.16,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,能带来幸福的龙尾的干物和天狗的胡子 不满意吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.61,0:14:30.27,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐把那个给小蚋吃掉了 是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.31,0:14:31.26,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,因为是干物嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.18,0:14:34.73,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,您还是给她正常点的礼物吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.80,0:14:38.93,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,快 一年级的赶紧集合 绕场五圈跑哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.21,0:14:40.51,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,明明还买了运动衣的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.97,0:14:43.11,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}一二 一二…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.60,0:14:42.59,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,连球场都不让进
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.89,0:14:53.69,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,是弓道部
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.97,0:14:55.25,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,好帅啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.85,0:15:02.40,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.62,0:15:05.24,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,草太 欢迎回来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.77,0:15:07.26,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 肚子饿了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.19,0:15:09.93,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了 姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.60,0:15:13.16,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,这杂物房一直都在这里有吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.33,0:15:13.94,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.55,0:15:17.84,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,这里没有一个井的祠堂吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.66,0:15:19.78,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.53,0:15:22.37,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,你们两个都回来了呀
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.66,0:15:23.41,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.81,0:15:25.16,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,井的祠堂啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.65,0:15:28.74,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,我们家神社可一直没有那种东西啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.61,0:15:30.72,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.49,0:15:33.92,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,我到底是怎么了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.51,0:15:35.53,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉有点奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.67,0:15:38.17,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,有消息
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.39,0:15:40.81,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,是北条同学发来的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.60,0:15:44.16,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,这个星期天要不要一起看电影？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.80,0:15:48.69,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.37,0:15:52.72,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,日暮 好久不见
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.41,0:15:57.06,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,学校还适应吗 男校怎么样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.24,0:15:58.81,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,全是男生
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.85,0:16:01.40,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.22,0:16:04.48,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,去看了电影 接着去了游戏中心玩
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.48,0:16:05.54,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,再一起吃了晚饭后就回家了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.07,0:16:07.50,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,已经交往了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.88,0:16:08.76,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,只是见了个面吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.17,0:16:11.07,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,这明显是约会嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.33,0:16:12.11,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,只是朋友哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.49,0:16:13.98,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.43,0:16:18.71,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,北条同学从初中开始就喜欢你了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.97,0:16:20.17,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,交往试试吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.52,0:16:21.89,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,你不讨厌他吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.15,0:16:24.63,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,不 不是那样的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.88,0:16:28.24,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 你没有什么其他喜欢的人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.77,0:16:29.27,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.09,0:16:56.77,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,不对
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.51,0:17:05.90,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,御神木上应该有个洞才对
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.92,0:17:09.18,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,洞 什么洞呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.71,0:17:15.62,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,犬…夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.67,0:17:20.18,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.50,0:17:24.25,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,五百年前 我在这棵树下和犬夜叉…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.31,0:17:31.72,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,食骨之井消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.96,0:17:33.72,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.90,0:17:34.57,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.80,0:17:35.81,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.37,0:17:38.67,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈 爷爷 草太
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.33,0:17:40.21,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.51,0:17:41.14,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.72,0:17:42.59,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.04,0:17:44.64,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,我在这里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.05,0:17:48.24,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,阿姨 戈薇怎么了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.45,0:17:52.60,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,她在哪里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.80,0:17:57.41,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都看不见我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.12,0:18:00.82,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,明明那么努力才考上的高中
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.18,0:18:02.89,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,却一天都没有去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.58,0:18:07.26,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,井已经被关闭了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.72,0:18:09.87,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,你已无处可去了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.17,0:18:13.26,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,四魂之玉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.80,0:18:15.43,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇 你在哪儿
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.20,0:18:19.35,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇应该在这冥道的某处才对
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.02,0:18:23.38,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}戈薇 姐姐 戈薇…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.00,0:18:25.61,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,这声音是戈薇的妈妈和弟弟的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.53,0:18:28.32,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇没有回去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.52,0:18:29.75,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,是犬夜叉吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.89,0:18:31.04,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,犬哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.14,0:18:35.93,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,等等 那声音…是戈薇的男朋友的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.40,0:18:40.63,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,食骨之井消失了 到底发生了什么事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.93,0:18:42.34,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇在哪儿
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.49,0:18:44.34,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.63,0:18:47.41,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,别担心 我一定会找到她的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.76,0:18:50.83,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,等着我 戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.84,0:18:55.70,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是哪儿 你对我做了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.79,0:19:00.52,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇 你一直都在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.27,0:19:04.45,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我明明在家里 还上了高中
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.46,0:19:06.68,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,那是你看到的幻象
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.94,0:19:10.64,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,你在那个世界应该要度过的今后的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.82,0:19:13.92,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,想要回到那个世界吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.65,0:19:16.99,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,那就许愿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.97,0:19:22.54,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,向我四魂之玉许愿 说你想要回到那个世界
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.10,0:19:25.19,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,要不然的话
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.51,0:19:29.67,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,你将孤身一人永久待在这片黑暗之中
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.50,0:19:36.95,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,碍事 风之伤
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.38,0:19:49.44,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,被打碎之后又变成了妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.93,0:19:51.07,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,这些家伙简直就像是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.12,0:19:57.12,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,不用去找 巫女不久就会到这儿的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.22,0:19:59.40,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,巫女 是指戈薇吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.00,0:20:05.07,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,能感觉得到 那个女人惧怕黑暗的内心
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.21,0:20:11.65,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈 爷爷 草太
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.91,0:20:13.18,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,谁都不在
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.58,0:20:19.19,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉 弥勒法师 珊瑚 七宝
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.61,0:20:20.70,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,谁也不会来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.87,0:20:22.85,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会这样
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.99,0:20:28.68,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇会屈服于对黑暗的恐惧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.03,0:20:30.50,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,必定会向玉许愿 希望得到救赎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.76,0:20:36.61,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,从所对抗的黑暗中逃离 想要回到和平的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.37,0:20:39.58,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,四魂之玉还存在吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.93,0:20:41.78,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,你没感觉到吗 半妖
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.42,0:20:45.96,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,你现在就处在四魂之玉之中
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.41,0:20:47.16,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,这里…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.17,0:20:54.27,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,而且戈薇许愿想要得救之后也将来到这里
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.32,0:20:54.82,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.46,0:20:57.57,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,在这四魂之玉之中
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.77,0:21:01.88,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇将永远持续地与我们战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.12,0:21:04.29,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,你想吞噬戈薇吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.59,0:21:07.95,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,四魂之玉是绝对不会消失的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.28,0:21:14.26,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,在玉中的战斗将永远持续 直到下一世再交给另一人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.37,0:21:18.56,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,与可悲的愿望同生 永远的轮回
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.86,0:21:21.06,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,因缘是无法斩断的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.18,0:21:26.79,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇 不要输 等我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.63,0:21:29.74,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.57,0:21:34.08,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,你不是属于战国时代的人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.91,0:21:38.87,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,回去 回到属于你的世界去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.82,0:21:45.15,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,若我许愿想回去的话 就能回去…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.82,0:21:51.79,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇 不要许愿
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.26,0:21:54.51,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇
